Package com.mapgroup.classificator.filemanager.reader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArffReader
    This class represents a specific way to read ARFF formatted file.
    DataReader
    This class represents the way to populate and create the whole system to manage the reading dataset.
    DataReaderFactory
    This class grant the possibility to generate a specific way to read the correct dataset formatted file based upon the type of file used.
    dbReader
    This class provide a way to populate the dataset from a table contained in a specific database.
    TxtReader
    This class grant the possibility to read the dataset from a textual file(extension '.txt').
    XlsReader
    This class grant the possibility to read the dataset information from an Excel file thanks to the Apache POI library functionality.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataReaderFactory.ReaderType
    Supported dataset file extensions
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IllegalTypeException
    Represents an error occurred while reading the dataset due to unrecognized attribute types.
